{"tid":2436544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3月7日︱66歲婦打科興疫苗後即胸口不適作嘔 45歲婦針後出疹 同被送院","createTime":"2021-03-07T08:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T08:50:54.000Z","uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26f11e9fbfb921421911f588fcc76b61b0b19c58","tid":2436544,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/KQ3GKHEKIZBKHODGGH4OBV363A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FKQ3GKHEKIZBKHODGGH4OBV363A%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=9010fdf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FKQ3GKHEKIZBKHODGGH4OBV363A%2F&h=e8029201\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/KQ3GKHEKIZBKHODGGH4OBV363A/</a><br />\n本港一周內出現兩宗接種科興疫苗後死亡個案，今日再有2名市民在官涌體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種科興疫苗後，感到不適，需要送院治理，據了解，2人目前情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒報道，接種中心醫務總監郭寶賢指，2人分別為45歲及66歲女子。45歲女子接種疫苗後，在該中心休息了30分鐘，並離開一段時間後，出現過敏反應，包括出疹，故返回中心求助。66歲女子則在接種疫苗數分鐘後，胸口不適及作嘔作悶。據悉，2人是分別接種疫苗，醫護人員觀察他們的情況後，決定將她們送院。"},{"pid":"3a5038a33c4a0727f35302e5ef107f4faf0f270a","tid":2436544,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"心理作用"},{"pid":"95ee16fc80340c63cab6656a7712c0a5522c76d0","tid":2436544,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgbFZH8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgbFZH8.png&h=3762c945&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7c089512dbf34a9362ebeb65f193ec7be5a99a4","tid":2436544,"uid":146948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"官涌又入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b63eabc7e95bdc6457246c0b20a270adea21ff","tid":2436544,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"